track_notes: Not so long, in summer take some water. Nice place in the National Park of the Verdon FFF-0034

You can park the car next to school, or if you want make it shorter 1km on the small road of Estang.
The path is ok until you reach the crest, arrived at the last bent, live the path and go up to the EST. Try to found a good way between vegetation, avoid inside the forest! then later, you must follow the crest tring to reach the big summital cairn. Plenty room for antenna.

nice summit to visit, but it is not so easy to found the right way. The last part of this track is off path! you must found by yourself the way to summit.
There is plenty room for antenna, and some wild animals on summit!
